ygData.msgSnippet: You have a beta account that you re not using?!?  I d be happy to take that off your hands, as I m having to share my beta account with 3 other people ... If
ygData.messageBody:
You have a beta account that you're not using?!? I'd be happy to take that
off your hands, as I'm having to share my beta account with 3 other people
:)

If you want to share, my email is osmosis@... :)

I played a Gnome enchanter on RZ, and so far it seems like there are some
similarities in DaoC, but the enchanter class is nowhere near as
versatile... the EQ class is spread out over several classes in Camelot.
I'm actually having the most fun playing a wizard-like character. Chain
casting takes on a new level, as you can begin casting a new spell as the
most recent one is happening. Excellent game, and I recommend the download.

-Cogg-
